Friday in a roadside bombing in south Lebanon, the Orient radio
reported.
</P>
<P>
The blast took place near the car of the killed SLA militiaman
when he was driving with his son along a road at Sabarh village in
the central province of Jezzine, an area policed by the SLA.
</P>
