<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, June 19 (Xinhua) -- The United States Friday called
an Israeli plan to strengthen its hold on Jerusalem "extremely
provocative."
</P>
<P>
Israel Thursday issued a plan that envisages widening
Jerusalem's boundaries to include land west of the city, in Israel
proper, and creating an "umbrella municipality" with
administrative powers over nearby town in Israel and some West
Bank settlements.
</P>
<P>
