ambassador to Belgium, Thanduyise Chiliza as ambassador to
Hungary, Timothy Maseko as high commissioner to Ghana and Johan
Kilian as ambassador to Peru.
</P>
<P>
Links, 51, who is ambassador to the European Union, will
combine that office with the Belgian ambassadorial post, to
become joint ambassador to the EU and Belgium.
</P>
<P>
South Africa is closing down 10 diplomatic missions owing to
budget cuts for foreign affairs. 
