it said that besides border criminal activities, border dispute
with India is also a major concern of Nepal.
</P>
<P>
In recent months, the Nepali side has been pressing India to
stop and return the Nepali territory encroached upon. In
particular, it demands the removal of Indian army from Kalapani in
far-western Nepal, which borders Nepal, India and China. 
