be a blessing for the German team at the France'98 World Cup finals.
</P>
<P>
Though German coach Berti Vogts is still pondering his team's
line-up against Yugoslavia, one thing is clear:the German team will
continue to play their pyhsical game despite the rash of red cards
handed out in the last two days.
</P>
<P>
