Cup, but their qualities are not so technical as in the past," said
Mihajlovic, "They have not so many individuals but they are still a
good team."
</P>
<P>
Yugoslav coach Slobodan Stantrac would not reveal his line-up in
the match against Germany:"Before the World Cup I said each line-up
would be picked according to each opponent and that is still the case."
