postgraduate science and technology courses will benefit annually.
About 400 teachers at postgraduate level will benefit from
pre-service and in-service training through international and
domestic programs as well as industrial secondment programs.
</P>
<P>
The Ministry of Science and Technology hopes to set up a
scholarship committee to prepare guidelines and administrative
procedures and to monitor and review the project's progress, the
paper added. 
