offer legal backing to the development of the country's High-tech
industry.
</P>
<P>
This suggestion came at the Third Plenary Meting of the Second
Session of the Standing Committee of the Ninth National Committee
of the Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference (CPPCC)
held yesterday in Beijing. 
</P>
